==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Undulating
<hw>Un"du*la`ting</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Rising and falling like
waves; resembling wave form or motion; undulatory; rolling; wavy;
<as>as, an <ex>undulating</ex> medium; <ex>undulating</ex>
ground</as>.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Un"du*la`ting*ly</wf>.
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Undulation</ent>⟦br⟧
